### 2.1 — Login as Org Admin
# → copy accessToken into @orgAdminToken above
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation { login(input: { email: \"orgadmin@gca.io\", password: \"OrgAdmin@123!\" }) { callResult { success message code result { accessToken refreshToken expiresAt } } } }"
}

###

### 2.2 — Verify Org Admin Identity
# → expect role = org_admin, scoped to GCA org
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{orgAdminToken}}

{
  "query": "query { me { userId organizationId fullName role permissions } }"
}

