### 2.3 — Create Domain: Cocoa Supply Chain
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{orgAdminToken}}

{
  "query": "mutation { createDomain(input: { organizationId: {{testOrgId}}, name: \"Cocoa Supply Chain\", code: \"cocoa\", description: \"End-to-end cocoa traceability from farm to export\" }) { callResult { success message code } } }"
}

###

### 2.4 — Query Domains (copy id into @domainId above)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{orgAdminToken}}

{
  "query": "query { domains { nodes { id name code isActive } } }"
}

###

### 2.5 — Create Stage 1: Harvesting
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{orgAdminToken}}

{
  "query": "mutation { createStage(input: { domainId: {{domainId}}, name: \"Harvesting\", code: \"harvesting\", sequence: 1, isRequired: true, description: \"Farm-level harvest and initial processing\" }) { callResult { success message code } } }"
}

###

### 2.6 — Create Stage 2: Aggregation
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{orgAdminToken}}

{
  "query": "mutation { createStage(input: { domainId: {{domainId}}, name: \"Aggregation\", code: \"aggregation\", sequence: 2, isRequired: true, description: \"Collection from farmers by licensed buyer\" }) { callResult { success message code } } }"
}

