### 2.7 — Create Stage 3: Processing
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{orgAdminToken}}

{
  "query": "mutation { createStage(input: { domainId: {{domainId}}, name: \"Processing\", code: \"processing\", sequence: 3, isRequired: false, description: \"Fermentation and drying at processing facility\" }) { callResult { success message code } } }"
}

###

### 2.8 — Create Stage 4: Export
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{orgAdminToken}}

{
  "query": "mutation { createStage(input: { domainId: {{domainId}}, name: \"Export\", code: \"export\", sequence: 4, isRequired: true, description: \"Final export preparation and shipment\" }) { callResult { success message code } } }"
}

