### 2.9 — Query Stages (copy ids into @stage1Id–@stage4Id above)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{orgAdminToken}}

{
  "query": "query { stages(order: { sequence: ASC }) { nodes { id name code sequence isRequired isActive } } }"
}

