### ==========================================================================

### 5.1 — Login as Field Agent
# → copy accessToken into @fieldAgentToken, refreshToken into @fieldAgentRefreshToken
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation { login(input: { email: \"agent@gca.io\", password: \"Agent@123!\" }) { callResult { success message code result { accessToken refreshToken expiresAt } } } }"
}

###

### 5.2 — Create Batch 1: GH-COC-2026-0001 (main happy-path batch)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{fieldAgentToken}}

{
  "query": "mutation { createBatch(input: { organizationId: {{testOrgId}}, domainId: {{domainId}}, productId: {{productId}}, batchCode: \"GH-COC-2026-0001\", originActorId: {{actor_kofiId}}, originDate: \"2026-04-20T06:00:00Z\", originLocation: \"{\\\"lat\\\":6.688,\\\"lng\\\":-1.624,\\\"region\\\":\\\"Ashanti\\\",\\\"community\\\":\\\"Atwima\\\"}\", initialQuantity: 500, initialUnitPrice: 1.50, metadata: null }) { callResult { success message code } } }"
}

###

