### ==========================================================================
### SECTION 7 — REJECTION FLOW: BATCH 2
### Tests: submit bad data → validator rejects → field agent corrects → validates
### ==========================================================================

### 7.1 — [Field Agent] Create StageRecord for Batch 2 with bad data (moisture=150%)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{fieldAgentToken}}

{
  "query": "mutation CreateSR($input: CreateStageRecordInput!) { createStageRecord(input: $input) { callResult { success message code } } }",
  "variables": {
    "input": {
      "batchId": {{batchId2}},
      "stageId": {{stage1Id}},
      "actorId": {{actor_kofiId}},
      "quantity": 320,
      "unitPrice": 1.45,
      "currency": "USD",
      "geoPoint": null,
      "notes": "Harvest data entry.",
      "recordedAt": "2026-04-21T09:00:00Z",
      "fields": [
        { "stageFieldId": {{sf_moistureId}}, "value": "150" },
        { "stageFieldId": {{sf_fermDaysId}}, "value": "5" },
        { "stageFieldId": {{sf_dryingId}}, "value": "sun_dried" }
      ]
    }
  }
}

###

### 7.2 — Query Stage Records for Batch 2 (copy id into @sr_rejectedId above)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{fieldAgentToken}}

{
  "query": "query { stageRecords(where: { batchId: { eq: {{batchId2}} } }) { nodes { id stageId status quantity fields { stageFieldId value } } } }"
}

###

### 7.3 — [Field Agent] Submit the Bad Record
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{fieldAgentToken}}

{
  "query": "mutation { submitStageRecord(input: { id: {{sr_rejectedId}} }) { callResult { success message code } } }"
}

###

### 7.4 — [Validator] Reject the Record
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{validatorToken}}

{
  "query": "mutation { rejectStageRecord(input: { id: {{sr_rejectedId}}, validationNotes: \"Moisture content of 150% is physically impossible. Please re-enter correct value.\" }) { callResult { success message code } } }"
}

###

### 7.5 — [Field Agent] Create Corrected StageRecord for Batch 2
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{fieldAgentToken}}

{
  "query": "mutation CreateSR($input: CreateStageRecordInput!) { createStageRecord(input: $input) { callResult { success message code } } }",
  "variables": {
    "input": {
      "batchId": {{batchId2}},
      "stageId": {{stage1Id}},
      "actorId": {{actor_kofiId}},
      "quantity": 320,
      "unitPrice": 1.45,
      "currency": "USD",
      "geoPoint": null,
      "notes": "Corrected record. Original moisture entry was a data entry error.",
      "recordedAt": "2026-04-21T09:00:00Z",
      "fields": [
        { "stageFieldId": {{sf_moistureId}}, "value": "8.1" },
        { "stageFieldId": {{sf_fermDaysId}}, "value": "5" },
        { "stageFieldId": {{sf_dryingId}}, "value": "sun_dried" }
      ]
    }
  }
}

